Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.80,0:00:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这么痛苦的回忆的话 我将不再向他人渴求什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.74,0:00:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十六岁的冬天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.67,0:00:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我体验了能撕裂身心的痛苦离别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.18,0:01:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)}白色花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.86,0:02:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又到圣诞节了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.57,0:02:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我与栞的初次相遇是在春天的某一日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.42,0:02:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天早晨 我比平常早了很多地来到了学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.02,0:02:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高中二年级的我对什么都感到厌烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.64,0:02:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是这个宛如天使牧场的学园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.05,0:02:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是带着纯真微笑的学生们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.90,0:02:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界一定是正确的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.99,0:02:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就是无法适应它的坏羔羊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.26,0:02:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救这样的我吧 阿门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.97,0:02:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.17,0:02:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.24,0:02:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么非得和大家一起笑不可？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.55,0:02:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么非得去听那些毫无兴趣的话题不可？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.41,0:02:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我保持着沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.71,0:02:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连做什么好或是想去做什么也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.53,0:03:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也别碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的事情全部忘掉吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.08,0:03:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的内心中没有一丝的滋润
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.94,0:03:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像一个人困在一片干涸的荒野中无路可走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.67,0:03:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.02,0:03:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着大人样的她 看起来全身充满着我所没有的滋润的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.66,0:03:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久保 栞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.20,0:03:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.18,0:03:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我还是第一次听到\n从你嘴里冒出别人的名字来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.70,0:03:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.97,0:03:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是今早认识了一个那样的一年级生而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.65,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的内心中 有什么东西正在开始变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.93,0:04:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.02,0:04:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣 你作为花蕾的自觉好像太少了一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 有稀客在呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.25,0:04:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.47,0:04:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.83,0:04:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为祥子长得跟日本娃娃一样漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.99,0:04:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不由自主地就想招待她一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我长得一副洋味十足的脸孔真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.37,0:04:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 闹别扭了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.27,0:04:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 我喜欢圣的脸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.22,0:04:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说也是凭脸孔选的妹妹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.56,0:04:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实不敢当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她曾说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.88,0:04:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“因为我想一直看着这张脸 所以请待在我身边”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.01,0:04:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为这一句话 我决定成为她的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.30,0:04:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我喜欢这样单纯而明快的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.22,0:04:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 从一开始姐姐对待我的方式就非常地高明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.78,0:04:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我变得连自已都吃惊的积极起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.06,0:04:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗？ 圣大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久保 栞同学今天休假了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.64,0:05:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.88,0:05:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想大概在圣堂那里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.99,0:05:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像理所当然似的栞出现在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.88,0:05:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为被这个世界所爱的洁白而闪耀的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.07,0:05:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安 白蔷薇的花蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.08,0:05:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份心情...会让你为难吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.99,0:05:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将自已完全地暴露 追寻着依靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完全不再有退路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.81,0:05:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直想着要见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.76,0:05:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于在这个学园里能遇见栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.40,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真想从心里对神说声感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.96,0:06:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在可利用的时间里我们都尽量单独相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.46,0:06:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我越来越远离蔷薇馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.02,0:06:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断陷入了栞的那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.59,0:06:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微保持一点距离不是更好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.06,0:06:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.36,0:06:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果想认妹妹 那到也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.51,0:06:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式地交与念珠 好好地向大家介绍一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.50,0:06:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会考虑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.39,0:06:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我可以走了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.69,0:06:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 一定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.96,0:06:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有打算认栞作妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.49,0:06:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐妹的仪式\n是那些没有像征就无法安心的人们做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从心底嘲笑着这一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.15,0:06:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.76,0:07:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概 我们双方各自都将\n与生俱来的双手连结到了同一个人的身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.63,0:07:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个结果就是将其它的东西完全地排除在外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.04,0:07:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被说了什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.84,0:07:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明仅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了吗？ 游泳的补习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.09,0:07:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.06,0:07:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在事故中丧失了双亲的栞一直住在学生宿舍里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.86,0:07:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个夏天 栞没有回到长崎的叔叔那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.71,0:07:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是留在了东京的某个修道院里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.57,0:08:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时在这里避避雨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.71,0:08:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.83,0:08:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没什么关系 擦擦你自已的头发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.65,0:08:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.87,0:08:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.40,0:09:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我们 会作为不同的个体出生到这个世上呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.05,0:09:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.48,0:09:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 你再睡一会儿也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.90,0:09:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨停了后我会叫醒你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.86,0:09:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.52,0:09:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨啊 别停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.34,0:09:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间就这样停止好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.07,0:09:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想与栞溶为一体然后消失掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种心情究竟是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向自已以外的人渴求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.69,0:09:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条路的前方又是哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个答案恐怕永远也找不到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 即使这样也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.25,0:10:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最真实的东西只有栞的悸动 体温和吐息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.91,0:10:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这些就是我所期望的这个世界的全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.47,0:10:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的心中栞的存在膨胀得越来越大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.55,0:10:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在蔷薇馆的时间变得越来越少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.59,0:10:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.98,0:10:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.92,0:10:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也想和你一起喝喝茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.96,0:10:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.26,0:10:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.08,0:11:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,断绝与我的姐妹之缘 重新找一个妹妹如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.61,0:11:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要违反约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.15,0:11:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我毕业以前 你可要好好地待在我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.75,0:11:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你不认妹妹 那也没什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.50,0:11:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走你自已不会后悔的路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在等我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.94,0:11:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别摆出那副表情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.14,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来就像我是瘟神一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.76,0:11:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是说教吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.85,0:11:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微冷静一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.94,0:11:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明对我们的事什么也不知道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.65,0:11:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你又知道栞同学什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.96,0:11:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“什么”是指...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.54,0:11:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得还是不要陷得太深为好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要特意来说这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.30,0:11:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不想看到你受伤的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.08,0:11:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会受伤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.83,0:11:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她如果不在了你会怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.62,0:12:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞会...不在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.33,0:12:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都没听到吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.88,0:12:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.53,0:12:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞同学毕业后会进入修道院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.49,0:12:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要成为修女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.41,0:12:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.05,0:12:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.26,0:12:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.83,0:12:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.71,0:12:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在进入这间学校之前就已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.50,0:12:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要隐瞒到现在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.54,0:12:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是没有机会说而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了也不会有什么改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然很喜欢栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.51,0:12:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你却不喜欢我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.53,0:12:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.82,0:12:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是个毕业前的陪伴… 你是这样随便地考虑的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.91,0:13:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.88,0:13:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会这么喜欢一个人也是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.60,0:13:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么要成为修女什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.06,0:13:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起我 你宁愿选择神吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.76,0:13:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是只有栞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.05,0:13:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要抛弃我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要像那样逼问我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.20,0:13:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为修女是我的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.86,0:13:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么不敢看着我的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是在迷惑吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.06,0:13:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.52,0:13:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞 我喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.31,0:13:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.43,0:13:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣母玛莉亚在看着我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.85,0:13:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是栞的回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.89,0:13:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我输给了圣母玛莉亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的上课态度变得失常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.77,0:14:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结业式的那天 我受到传唤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.29,0:14:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是栞的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.91,0:14:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟她已经再没有什么关系了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.55,0:14:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐藤同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.45,0:14:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久保 栞也是这样说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是自已的错之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.81,0:14:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞也被叫来这里了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.36,0:14:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一头陷入一样东西中而看不清周围 不是一件很寂寞的事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.33,0:14:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞两日前提出了外宿申请 无论在宿舍还是修道院都找不到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.37,0:14:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞 怎样才能见到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.26,0:14:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.98,0:14:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.41,0:14:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.14,0:14:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在蔷薇馆会开一个联欢会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.57,0:14:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令会为大家做好吃的饼干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有心情的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞 好想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.69,0:15:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.74,0:15:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.82,0:15:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在见不着你的时候 我只是想着你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.67,0:15:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使做祈祷 也没法让你的样子离开脑海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.27,0:15:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园长非常担心我们的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.31,0:15:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也做过约定不再见面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.85,0:15:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞 一起逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.83,0:15:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.83,0:15:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在未知的土地上 不被任何人打扰的活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.66,0:15:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.99,0:15:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿意吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会不愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要和圣在一起 到哪里都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.75,0:16:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.43,0:16:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾好行李就过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.13,0:16:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在车站等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.06,0:16:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会儿见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞微笑着目送我而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.39,0:16:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法忘记那个微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.63,0:16:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.45,0:16:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定的时间已过去3小时了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.51,0:17:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞已经不会来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.76,0:17:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我仍无法离开月台的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.00,0:17:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是无法舍弃也许栞\n马上就会从那个楼梯下来的仅有的一点希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.47,0:17:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是做梦 我也想见到栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.86,0:17:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.80,0:17:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.85,0:17:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.81,0:17:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我代替栞同学来接你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.80,0:17:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞同学好像不会与你一起走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.03,0:17:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.58,0:17:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞同学好像曾经来过这个车站一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.55,0:17:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从远处注视着在月台上的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.31,0:18:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后觉得果然还是不能这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.66,0:18:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然来了为什么不直接...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.45,0:18:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见面后会让决心变弱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.98,0:18:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变弱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然她看起来很有大人样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但毕竟仍只是高中一年级生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.33,0:18:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会动摇也是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.87,0:18:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞会去哪里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.26,0:18:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 听说会转学到很远的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是她接受了的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.70,0:18:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.28,0:18:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.44,0:18:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有遇见我的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.70,0:18:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够相遇是件好事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.83,0:18:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能创造可以坦然回想着\n“能够相遇真好”的未来 那么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.57,0:18:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种未来一定无法来临的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.02,0:18:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤痕总有一天会愈合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.54,0:18:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 你不是还有我在身边吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.73,0:18:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会是真以为我只爱着你的脸孔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.71,0:18:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.33,0:18:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是失礼 那只是为了不增加你负担的一个方便的借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.81,0:19:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对待你的方式可是很高明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.80,0:19:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.77,0:19:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是姐姐不是就要毕业了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.90,0:19:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会担心你的可不只是我一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.18,0:19:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.99,0:19:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你担心真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.02,0:19:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.63,0:19:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是令做的饼干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.96,0:19:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.51,0:19:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.72,0:19:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.77,0:19:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.23,0:19:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才已经向圣的母亲打了电话说你要住下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.88,0:19:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.72,0:19:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闲话少说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.17,0:19:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从明天开始就是开心的寒假了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就玩到深夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安安静静地闹它一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.16,0:19:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日期已经变了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.83,0:19:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.29,0:19:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.72,0:20:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞前夜过去 我知道自己已是十七岁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.15,0:20:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.75,0:20:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.08,0:20:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人也来帮忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.35,0:20:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.41,0:20:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日诚子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.83,0:20:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 也就是须加星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.02,0:20:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去大波斯菊编缉部时 曾见过面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.14,0:20:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.15,0:20:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉前段时间失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.42,0:20:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.22,0:20:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的学生给您添了不少麻烦真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.30,0:20:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.74,0:20:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是佐藤 圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.14,0:21:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 你就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.60,0:21:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 今天是...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.14,0:21:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来见学园长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.12,0:21:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那么 我来为您带路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 我知道路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.66,0:21:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟过去一点也没变啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.82,0:21:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.45,0:21:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉安的毕业生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.83,0:21:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 据说已知道香织还活着的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.21,0:21:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是要在圣诞前夜去见香织的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.51,0:21:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就是说香织在这里了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.30,0:21:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 也许是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.59,0:21:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 去见学园长是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.15,0:21:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 是这样啊 学园长就是香织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.27,0:21:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.45,0:21:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么两个人在隔了这么多年后终于可以再见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.24,0:21:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.65,0:21:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联欢会要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.19,0:21:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.44,0:21:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.75,0:21:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.26,0:21:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.24,0:22:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.28,0:22:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.09,0:22:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是我的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.84,0:22:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My Happy Birthday
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.95,0:23:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从波折的姐妹宣言开始 终于到了现在这个时候
